# 0.5

- Add non generic `IValidatableValue` interface (implemented explicit in the base class)
- Refactor the `RevalidateOtherValueValidationRule` rule to use nongeneric valaidatable values for trigger

## 0.4

- Add `IsNotValid` property for easier error visibility binding 
- Add GreaterThan rule
- Add SmallerThan rule
- Add RefreshValidation rule

## 0.3

- Add smaple project
    - Xamarin.Forms (iOS, Android, UWP, macOS, WPF)
- Add more meta information to assembly
    - Build date
    - Semantic version
    - Git hash
- New Validators
    - RegexValidationRule
    - NullValidationRule<T>
    - PhoneNumberValidationrule
    - EmailValidationRule

## 0.2

- Add requred rule
- Add contains rule

